These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, chess, card-games, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, action, epic, mystery
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, van, snowmobile
1. the person driving the taxi is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking      | magic-tricks | chess | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | scientific  | action   | mystery    |
| Transport     | taxi     | van    | snowmobile    | skateboard      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, fishing, magic-tricks, puzzles
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, colombian, indian, malaysian
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, ship, skateboard, bus
1. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the indian##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the colombian##1
7. the spanish is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
8. the malaysian is between the colombian and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles | magic-tricks   | fishing | woodworking  |
| Nationality   | indian     | spanish | malaysian  | colombian |
| Transport     | bus        | skateboard  | ship    | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, apple, spinach, pepper
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, brazilian, mexican, french
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, car, skateboard
1. the french is between the person eating pomegranate and the person eating pepper##2
2. the brazilian is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the scooter is the person eating spinach##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
5. the person eating pepper is in an odd position##4
6. the mexican is between the person eating apple and the italian##2
7. the french is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | pomegranate | apple   | pepper     | spinach     |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | french | mexican   | italian  |
| Transport     | skateboard      | tram | car | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, zombie, documentary, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, ambient, rock, folk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, ice-hockey, handball, lacrosse
1. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
2. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
5. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is the fan of r&b##1
7. the fan of rock is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | satire   | documentary     | zombie |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | folk      | r&b        | ambient     |
| Sport         | handball | weightlifting | lacrosse | ice-hockey   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, dutch, malaysian, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, weightlifting, soccer, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, trike, ship, airplane
1. the australian is the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the malaysian is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
7. the dutch is on the far right##1
8. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian   | malaysian | dutch |
| Sport         | weightlifting      | badminton | cycling      | soccer |
| Transport     | trike | subway        | airplane       | ship  |

