.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, apple, carrot, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, collecting
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, cat, rabbit
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating apple##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
6. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating apple##1
7. the person eating plum is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | carrot   | plum      | apple       | nectarine |
| Hobby   | card-games | collecting | singing     | photography |
| Pet     | rabbit     | turtle  | goldfish | cat |

