.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, mirinda, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, drama, western
4 different pets are kept: hamster, ferret, fish, cat
1. the owner of the fish is the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the owner of the ferret is between the person watching western movies and the owner of the hamster##2
3. the person watching western movies is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
5. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is the person drinking juice##1
8. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda   | sprite          | cola | juice        |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | spy | western   | mystery     |
| Pet           | hamster | ferret         | cat         | fish |

