.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, gardening, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, nurse, doctor, coach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, funk, pop, r&b
1. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
2. the doctor is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the coach is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of funk is between the chef and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
6. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the doctor##3
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | fishing      | gardening       | photography    |
| Job           | nurse  | doctor  | coach | chef |
| Music-Genre   | r&b      | pop | funk         | blues    |

