.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, project-manager, musician, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, cricket, soy-milk-polo, rowing
1. the journalist is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the journalist##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the journalist##3
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soy-milk-polo##3
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the journalist##1
7. the journalist is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the project-manager is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
9. the firefighter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | milk         | lemonade  | juice     | soy-milk         |
| Job        | firefighter | project-manager | journalist | musician         |
| Sport      | cricket         | soy-milk-polo  | skateboarding   | rowing |

