.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, funk, blues, metal
There are 4 different nationalities: american, polish, argentine, indian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, fish, guinea-pig
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
 2. the american is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 4. the argentine is between the fan of funk and the fan of pop##2
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the fan of blues##1
 7. the indian is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
 9. the polish is between the fan of metal and the fan of blues##2
10. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | blues    | funk | metal    |
| Nationality   | american | argentine | polish  | indian |
| Pet           | fish   | guinea-pig    | ferret        | frog   |

