.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, milk, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, doctor, designer, security-guard
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, egyptian, polish
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
2. the doctor is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the polish is on the left or right of the designer##3
4. the doctor is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the project-manager##1
6. the polish is on the right of the doctor##1
7. the canadian is on the left of the doctor##1
8. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the canadian##3
9. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | sprite                | cola  | lemonade | milk   |
| Job           | security-guard | doctor | project-manager   | designer |
| Nationality   | canadian         | japanese     | polish     | egyptian |

