.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, orange, cucumber, potato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, spy, comedy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, metal, folk, hip-hop
1. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the fan of soul is between the person watching mystery movies and the fan of hip-hop##2
6. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | cucumber    | orange  | potato  | lemon |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy | family | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | soul     | hip-hop    | metal |

