.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, chinese, brazilian, canadian
4 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, cat, hedgehog
1. the owner of the mouse is between the person drinking iced-tea and the indonesian##2
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
7. the indonesian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
8. the brazilian is the person drinking mirinda##1
9. the canadian is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | iced-tea      | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk    |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | chinese | canadian | indonesian |
| Pet           | hedgehog      | cat       | mouse   | bird      |

