.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, drawing, fishing, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, turkish, american, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, snowboarding, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's sport is badminton##2
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the egyptian is between the person who's sport is badminton and the spanish##2
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
8. the turkish is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading    | fishing | drawing  | writing  |
| Nationality   | american | turkish       | egyptian | spanish |
| Sport         | snowboarding   | badminton      | baseball | soccer       |

