.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, fanta, lemonade
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, fantasy, action, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, goldfish, frog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person drinking fanta is the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the owner of the frog is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | fanta      | soy-milk | coffee     | lemonade    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | zombie      | fantasy | action |
| Pet           | goldfish   | hedgehog  | dog     | frog |

