.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, sprite, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skateboarding, weightlifting, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, subway, roller
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person drinking fanta is between the person driving the boat and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
6. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | sprite    | fanta     | hot-chocolate    | juice        |
| Sport       | weightlifting   | climbing | skateboarding | badminton |
| Transport   | roller | subway      | boat    | skateboard   |

