.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, cranberry, orange, pepper
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, adventure, sports, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, italian, polish, dutch
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
2. the spanish is between the italian and the person eating pepper##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
4. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
5. the spanish is on the left of the italian##1
6. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
7. the polish is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating pepper is the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | cranberry | pepper  | banana   | orange    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | sports     | thriller | adventure |
| Nationality   | polish   | dutch | spanish | italian   |

