4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the person watching spy movies is the thai##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the egyptian##1
7. the egyptian is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
8. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | spy | superhero   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | metal   | salsa     | dubstep    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | egyptian | thai  | british |

