.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, mango, zucchini, corn
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, chess, sudoku, collecting
4 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, hamster, dog
1. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
4. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
5. the person eating mango is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | zucchini    | mango    | apricot  | corn |
| Hobby   | collecting | chess | singing | sudoku      |
| Pet     | rabbit   | fish        | dog   | hamster       |

 